      • reloadPrefs

        public static void reloadPrefs()
        This is called upon opening the prefs window, canceling changes, or closing the prefs window to ensure that only saved preferences are used. However, if the user changes the prefs and leaves the window open without saving, the current changes are used by JEX until canceling or closing
